pull.title: [Qt] minor optimisations in peertablemodel
pull.body:
- remove an unneeded include of net.h in peertablemodel.cpp
- add const after size() in PeerTablePriv
- remove 2x unneeded else in functions
- replace a (int) typecast by (QVariant) to use Qt style

issue.title: [Qt] allow banning and unbanning over UI->peers table
issue.body:
This adds 4 ban options to the peers tables context menu (1h, 24h, 7d, 365d). If there are active bans, a table with banned subnets will be shown.
Sync between the rpc bans and the ui bans are guaranteed over a new `uiInterface` signal.

Screenshots:
